115
00:08:17,230 --> 00:08:17,820
One silver coin.

116
00:08:17,820 --> 00:08:20,150
Book of Wisdom, don't lose in life.

117
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:21,980
Whether you're leading soldiers to war

118
00:08:21,980 --> 00:08:22,950
