146
00:09:26,030 --> 00:09:26,990
This is nice.

147
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,050
This is cheap.

148
00:09:28,050 --> 00:09:28,820
Lord Xiu.

149
00:09:30,190 --> 00:09:31,590
