156
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:50,770
Your first time?

157
00:09:51,430 --> 00:09:52,030
Not bad.

158
00:09:55,170 --> 00:09:56,300
It's really not bad.

159
00:10:01,070 --> 00:10:01,930
