162
00:10:08,080 --> 00:10:08,430
What?

163
00:10:09,690 --> 00:10:11,820
To ask you to help us get our stuff back.

164
00:10:13,530 --> 00:10:14,590
Ze, let me tell you.

165
00:10:15,230 --> 00:10:17,960
The stuff in the stall belongs to the stall owner,

166
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,990
not me, Zichuan Xiu.

167
00:10:20,310 --> 00:10:21,660
Go back and tell everyone

168
00:10:21,660 --> 00:10:23,120
if the goods in the stalls got stolen

169
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,560
and they can't get the money,

170
00:10:24,560 --> 00:10:27,460
that means they can't get the money at the end of the year.

171
00:10:27,460 --> 00:10:29,380
What are you waiting for? Go!

172
00:10:31,750 --> 00:10:33,710
Make way.

173
00:10:34,830 --> 00:10:38,160
Are you really not in a hurry? Aren't you going to take a look?

174
00:10:38,790 --> 00:10:40,630
Actually, for the Xiu Battalion,

175
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:42,310
this is a rare opportunity.

176
00:10:43,710 --> 00:10:44,870
Now, everyone thinks

177
00:10:44,870 --> 00:10:47,590
the Xiu Battalion is full of loose cannons and won't make it.

178
00:10:47,590 --> 00:10:50,390
But under certain conditions...

179
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:52,430
The premise of these conditions

180
00:10:52,430 --> 00:10:53,880
is that they can truly understand

181
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,160
what they really want.

182
00:10:56,750 --> 00:10:59,460
