186
00:11:13,990 --> 00:11:14,460
Stop!

187
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:15,830
Don't run!

188
00:11:16,030 --> 00:11:16,470
Come on!

189
00:11:16,470 --> 00:11:16,870
Stop!

190
00:11:16,990 --> 00:11:18,070
Come on!

191
00:11:18,070 --> 00:11:19,070
Stop right there!

192
00:11:20,220 --> 00:11:21,110
What are you waiting for?

193
00:11:21,110 --> 00:11:22,030
Beat them up!

194
00:11:22,390 --> 00:11:23,710
I'll beat you to death!

195
00:11:25,340 --> 00:11:25,860
