202
00:11:42,500 --> 00:11:43,300
So serious?

203
00:11:47,570 --> 00:11:49,410
The art of war is to be cunning.

204
00:11:49,750 --> 00:11:50,390
Brothers!

205
00:11:51,590 --> 00:11:52,630
Ho-ho-ha!

206
00:11:52,860 --> 00:11:53,790
Ho-ho-ha!

207
00:11:54,060 --> 00:11:56,200
Ho-ho-ha!

208
00:11:57,640 --> 00:11:59,320
Kill!

209
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:01,730
Wait. Watch out for traps.

210
00:12:04,220 --> 00:12:04,940
Well,

211
00:12:05,350 --> 00:12:07,150
