219
00:12:23,360 --> 00:12:25,120
We'll split the profit 30/70.

220
00:12:26,050 --> 00:12:28,420
It'll be a lot more than these peanuts.

221
00:12:31,070 --> 00:12:32,870
Okay, I'll give you another one.

222
00:12:34,580 --> 00:12:35,020
Boss.

223
00:12:35,270 --> 00:12:35,830
