224
00:12:36,070 --> 00:12:36,510
Boss!

225
00:12:36,870 --> 00:12:37,440
Here.

226
00:12:39,390 --> 00:12:40,030
Boss.

227
00:12:40,630 --> 00:12:42,510
We took back all the stolen items.

228
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:45,120
Really? Did you all work together?

229
00:12:45,150 --> 00:12:45,990
Of course.

230
00:12:46,910 --> 00:12:48,360
That's our money.

231
00:13:01,310 --> 00:13:02,510
Come on.

232
00:13:02,830 --> 00:13:03,390
Cheers.

233
00:13:03,840 --> 00:13:04,470
Cheers.

234
00:13:07,710 --> 00:13:08,550
Not bad.

235
00:13:09,710 --> 00:13:10,570
Have some meat.

236
00:13:10,730 --> 00:13:11,990
I'll fill it up for you.

237
00:13:12,230 --> 00:13:12,630
Well,

238
00:13:13,860 --> 00:13:16,750
