240
00:13:24,230 --> 00:13:25,230
Sit down and talk.

241
00:13:26,400 --> 00:13:29,210
Miss Baichuan, have a seat.

242
00:13:38,150 --> 00:13:39,200
Did it say

243
00:13:39,710 --> 00:13:41,320
