245
00:13:44,160 --> 00:13:45,430
Oh no.

246
00:13:45,840 --> 00:13:48,840
What's wrong? Are the Three Central Offices so scary?

247
00:13:48,990 --> 00:13:51,650
Let me tell you, these Three Central Offices...

248
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:57,900
Ning knows our family history better.

249
00:13:57,930 --> 00:14:00,290
So, let her tell us about it.

250
00:14:03,580 --> 00:14:04,700
It all started

251
00:14:05,350 --> 00:14:08,390
a long, long time ago.

252
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,130
A hero of his generation, Zichuan Yun,

253
00:14:11,310 --> 00:14:13,270
