257
00:14:19,590 --> 00:14:21,190
got worse and worse.

258
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:22,710
Gradually,

259
00:14:22,730 --> 00:14:24,190
he could no longer serve

260
00:14:24,190 --> 00:14:25,790
as Zichuan's ruler.

261
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:29,200
