262
00:14:29,350 --> 00:14:30,550
and domineering.

263
00:14:30,710 --> 00:14:31,590
Come in.

264
00:14:34,110 --> 00:14:36,430
General Ming Lan was a great warrior.

265
00:14:36,670 --> 00:14:38,990
On the day he returned victorious,

266
00:14:39,590 --> 00:14:40,990
