267
00:14:41,870 --> 00:14:43,630
Lord Chieftain, I’m back.

268
00:14:43,840 --> 00:14:46,090
You dirtied my carpet.

269
00:14:47,710 --> 00:14:49,270
Drag him out and behead him.

270
00:14:49,520 --> 00:14:51,640
Lord Chieftain, I didn’t mean it.

271
00:14:55,430 --> 00:14:56,710
How cruel!

272
00:14:58,310 --> 00:15:00,190
The general who stepped on the carpet

273
00:15:00,190 --> 00:15:01,680
