274
00:15:01,680 --> 00:15:04,390
and was beheaded just like that when he returned.

275
00:15:04,390 --> 00:15:05,090
He was beheaded?

276
00:15:05,090 --> 00:15:05,830
He was beheaded just like that?

277
00:15:05,830 --> 00:15:08,630
Who would have thought that

278
00:15:08,630 --> 00:15:10,920
his last words to his son before he passed away

279
00:15:10,920 --> 00:15:11,870
would be...

280
00:15:14,030 --> 00:15:14,510
What?

281
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:15,330
Remember to...

282
00:15:15,330 --> 00:15:17,800
Remember to clean your shoes.

283
00:15:18,620 --> 00:15:19,420
Shoes?

284
00:15:19,440 --> 00:15:21,840
What's more bizarre is that the next day...

285
00:15:23,380 --> 00:15:25,990
Why hasn't Ming Lan come to see me yet?

286
00:15:27,710 --> 00:15:29,390
I've been waiting for him.

