00:15:30,660 --> 00:15:33,350
Is he disrespecting me

288
00:15:33,980 --> 00:15:36,690
because he has great military achievements now?

289
00:15:36,690 --> 00:15:37,620
Lord Chieftain,

290
00:15:37,730 --> 00:15:39,750
do you remember what happened yesterday?

291
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:40,670
Yesterday?

292
00:15:41,910 --> 00:15:42,750
Zichuan Yun.

293
00:15:42,910 --> 00:15:43,910
His amnesia

294
00:15:43,910 --> 00:15:45,510
was getting worse and worse.

295
00:15:45,890 --> 00:15:49,440
Everyone in the family, whether they were officials or nobles,

296
00:15:49,510 --> 00:15:52,550
were all afraid of receiving his orders.

297
00:15:57,440 --> 00:15:58,830
Long time no see.

298
00:15:59,070 --> 00:16:00,730
Come in and play chess with me.

299
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:15,220
Assassin! You entered without announcing your presence.

300
00:16:15,220 --> 00:16:17,150
Are you trying to assassinate me?

301
00:16:17,620 --> 00:16:18,980
No, Lord Chieftain.

302
00:16:19,270 --> 00:16:20,430
You asked me to come!

303
00:16:20,460 --> 00:16:22,580
Guards! Kill the assassin!

304
00:16:26,670 --> 00:16:28,580
Under Zichuan Yun's authority,

305
00:16:28,670 --> 00:16:31,070
all the officials and nobles in this family

306
00:16:31,140 --> 00:16:33,650
lived in fear, trembling.

307
00:16:34,510 --> 00:16:35,480
In everyone's heart,

308
00:16:35,480 --> 00:16:36,650
was a wish

309
00:16:36,870 --> 00:16:38,670
that they couldn't speak about.

310
00:16:38,710 --> 00:16:39,790
Could it be...

311
00:16:42,510 --> 00:16:44,110
When power is too concentrated

312
00:16:44,110 --> 00:16:45,350
on one person

313
00:16:45,790 --> 00:16:47,250
and no one can control him,

314
00:16:47,270 --> 00:16:49,350
it's scary, isn't it?

315
00:16:49,380 --> 00:16:50,430
That's right.

316
00:16:50,450 --> 00:16:51,690
You see, I'm not so bad at this.

317
00:16:51,690 --> 00:16:52,950
Should I tell the story then?

318
00:16:52,950 --> 00:16:53,630
Sure.

319
00:16:53,770 --> 00:16:55,950
So, after the new Chieftain Zichuan Heng

320
00:16:55,950 --> 00:16:56,850
inherited the position,

321
00:16:56,850 --> 00:16:58,960
he joined forces with the nobles,

322
00:16:59,150 --> 00:17:01,350
changed Zichuan's political system

323
00:17:01,550 --> 00:17:04,010
and established the Three Central Offices.

324
00:17:04,430 --> 00:17:04,890
This...

325
00:17:04,910 --> 00:17:05,510
Is that so?

326
00:17:06,950 --> 00:17:09,630
The Three Central Offices is made up of

327
00:17:09,630 --> 00:17:10,990
centers of nobles from all the provinces.

328
00:17:10,990 --> 00:17:13,829
It has the right to supervise the family administration.

329
00:17:13,829 --> 00:17:14,869
With regards to the Chieftain's decisions,

330
00:17:14,869 --> 00:17:16,190
if they have any objections,

331
00:17:16,190 --> 00:17:17,950
they can propose amendments.

332
