When necessary,

333
00:17:19,160 --> 00:17:21,670
they can impeach the Chieftain and replace him.

334
00:17:21,670 --> 00:17:22,270
Of course,

335
00:17:22,390 --> 00:17:24,710
in order to preserve the bloodline of Zichuan,

336
00:17:24,710 --> 00:17:26,210
Zichuan Yun added another clause

337
00:17:26,210 --> 00:17:29,410
stating that no matter who you change the Chieftain to,

338
00:17:29,540 --> 00:17:31,190
this position must be filled

339
