362
00:18:22,070 --> 00:18:24,030
Those grand suggestions

363
00:18:24,780 --> 00:18:25,790
are just for

364
00:18:25,820 --> 00:18:27,670
the personal interests of those nobles.

365
00:18:27,670 --> 00:18:29,530
They never represent the people.

366
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:35,390
Today, the Three Central Offices

367
00:18:35,390 --> 00:18:37,070
has become a bloated system.

368
00:18:38,190 --> 00:18:39,310
