374
00:18:54,630 --> 00:18:56,290
and they want us to return now.

375
00:18:57,330 --> 00:18:58,610
This is ridiculous.

376
00:18:58,640 --> 00:19:00,620
Maybe the Ministry of War has some long-term considerations.

377
00:19:00,620 --> 00:19:02,150
What long-term considerations?

378
00:19:02,150 --> 00:19:04,550
This decision of theirs is short-sighted.

379
00:19:05,760 --> 00:19:08,290
This is a document from the Imperial Capital.

380
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:18,260
I see.

381
00:19:24,100 --> 00:19:27,820
Looks like we have to return to the Imperial Capital.

382
00:19:28,190 --> 00:19:29,660
Can we delay the return

383
00:19:29,820 --> 00:19:31,390
on the grounds that we're holding the line?

384
00:19:31,390 --> 00:19:34,730
Will Three Central Offices be delayed because of me?

385
00:19:35,040 --> 00:19:36,120
Why are we having

386
00:19:36,380 --> 00:19:38,350
a Three Central Offices meeting in the middle of the war?

387
00:19:38,350 --> 00:19:40,350
These advisors were all nobles.

388
00:19:41,030 --> 00:19:43,560
They have lucrative businesses in Yuanzhou.

389
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:45,280
Now, with all the fighting,

390
00:19:45,550 --> 00:19:48,800
their financial resources will continue to be depleted.

391
00:19:51,360 --> 00:19:53,080
