396
00:20:29,670 --> 00:20:30,510
I'll meet you.

397
00:20:31,130 --> 00:20:31,550
Yes.

398
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:40,400
If you want to leave, go by yourself. I'm not leaving.

399
00:20:41,480 --> 00:20:44,550
But Wen He is already here.

400
00:20:45,270 --> 00:20:46,130
Your Highness.

401
00:20:46,350 --> 00:20:48,230
I've been ordered by Lord Chieftain to escort the Princess.

402
00:20:48,230 --> 00:20:48,750
Now...

403
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:51,790
Stop. I know what you want to say.

404
00:20:52,660 --> 00:20:53,990
But if you say it,

405
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:56,120
I won't have any time left.

406
00:20:58,260 --> 00:21:00,730
One day? I only need one day.

407
00:21:03,550 --> 00:21:05,230
Okay, one day.

408
00:21:10,810 --> 00:21:11,770
One day.

409
00:21:17,060 --> 00:21:20,180
I understand. The war is not over and Lei Hong is not dead

410
00:21:20,830 --> 00:21:23,290
so you won't return to the Imperial Capital.

411
00:21:23,710 --> 00:21:26,280
I'll stay until you've quelled the rebellion

412
00:21:26,310 --> 00:21:27,440
and killed Lei Hong,

413
00:21:27,760 --> 00:21:30,320
then we'll go back together, okay?

414
00:21:32,960 --> 00:21:35,830
Brother Xiu, as long as I can be with you,

415
00:21:35,950 --> 00:21:37,550
I can stay in Yuanzhou

416
00:21:37,550 --> 00:21:38,880
for another year or two.

417
00:21:38,950 --> 00:21:40,390
A year or two.

418
00:21:42,310 --> 00:21:43,830
What about 20 or 30 years?

419
00:21:47,070 --> 00:21:49,950
Ning, this land, Yuanzhou,

420
00:21:49,990 --> 00:21:53,390
a place that countless people depend on for their livelihood.

421
00:21:53,390 --> 00:21:55,190
