425
00:22:03,150 --> 00:22:03,950
Everything.

426
00:22:07,640 --> 00:22:08,320
Ning.

427
00:22:12,560 --> 00:22:13,860
I'm just kidding.

428
00:22:15,070 --> 00:22:17,030
If I have to stay in Yuanzhou for another year or two years,

429
00:22:17,030 --> 00:22:17,820
I won't be able to stand it.

430
00:22:17,820 --> 00:22:19,350
There are so many bugs here.

431
00:22:20,690 --> 00:22:23,810
There are so many things in the family now.

432
00:22:24,940 --> 00:22:26,710
The Imperial Capital is going to have the Three Central Offices meeting soon.

433
00:22:26,710 --> 00:22:28,970
And you have to suppress the rebels here.

434
00:22:29,750 --> 00:22:32,280
I'm just causing you trouble by staying here.

435
00:22:33,060 --> 00:22:34,430
I... I'll return.

436
00:22:35,450 --> 00:22:36,090
Ning.

437
00:22:36,310 --> 00:22:37,380
I'm not finished.

438
00:22:37,810 --> 00:22:39,250
But if I want to go back,

439
00:22:39,280 --> 00:22:42,320
you have to pick a good horse for me personally.

440
00:22:42,610 --> 00:22:43,890
And you'll help me

441
00:22:43,990 --> 00:22:45,950
pack all my luggage.

442
00:22:46,750 --> 00:22:48,870
I've suffered a lot along the way.

443
00:22:48,910 --> 00:22:50,770
I must be comfortable on the road.

444
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:56,390
Okay, everything you want me to do,

445
00:22:56,460 --> 00:22:57,520
I'll listen to you.

446
00:22:58,460 --> 00:22:59,590
