447
00:23:25,740 --> 00:23:26,340
Ning.

448
00:24:07,670 --> 00:24:11,150
I'm willing to leave, even with a smile on my face.

449
00:24:12,260 --> 00:24:14,460
I hope you can come back with a smile too.

450
00:24:15,450 --> 00:24:17,650
I won't say I'm waiting for you anymore.

451
00:24:18,190 --> 00:24:19,720
But I hope you can come back.

452
00:24:21,500 --> 00:24:24,860
My dear Brother Xiu, this is not a farewell.

453
00:24:25,940 --> 00:24:27,300
This is our beginning.

454
00:24:33,290 --> 00:24:35,170
Lord Si Yilin will meet us later.

455
00:24:35,790 --> 00:24:38,680
Your Highness, we can't tell anyone about this trip.

456
00:24:38,680 --> 00:24:40,230
You'll have to suffer a little

457
00:24:40,230 --> 00:24:41,960
and pretend to be an attendant.

458
00:25:14,870 --> 00:25:16,130
