462
00:25:24,930 --> 00:25:27,160
I'm looking for the way to Bulu Village.

463
00:25:27,950 --> 00:25:29,380
We're leaving for Bulu Village tomorrow.

464
00:25:29,380 --> 00:25:30,580
Go back and get ready.

465
00:26:10,220 --> 00:26:11,500
De Lun, you're back.

466
00:26:12,200 --> 00:26:14,600
You silly boy. You're so tall now.

467
00:26:14,850 --> 00:26:16,830
