484
00:27:11,540 --> 00:27:12,410
You're back.

485
00:27:16,150 --> 00:27:17,150
You're back!

486
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:20,850
Xiu, thank you for sending us home.

487
00:27:21,480 --> 00:27:23,390
Thank you.

488
00:27:23,470 --> 00:27:25,350
Thank you, Xiu!

489
00:27:25,620 --> 00:27:28,750
Congratulations on returning to your hometown. Cheers!

490
00:27:28,750 --> 00:27:29,910
Cheers!

491
00:27:30,420 --> 00:27:31,130
Thank you.

