00:27:41,750 --> 00:27:42,080
Here.

498
00:27:42,250 --> 00:27:45,410
Xiu, there are wars going on outside.

499
00:27:45,590 --> 00:27:48,770
Why don't you stay here for a while

500
00:27:48,800 --> 00:27:49,640
and lay low?

501
00:27:50,150 --> 00:27:52,470
Bulu Village is not only our hometown,

502
00:27:52,760 --> 00:27:55,290
