532
00:29:04,470 --> 00:29:05,890
That's why Lord Xiu sent Shaozi

533
00:29:05,890 --> 00:29:07,110
to follow this clue

534
00:29:07,690 --> 00:29:09,350
and expose the other threads.

535
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:11,130
The final buyer was indeed him.

536
00:29:56,180 --> 00:29:56,690
My Lord.

537
00:29:57,110 --> 00:29:59,430
We'll be closer to the North Clan after this hill.

538
00:29:59,430 --> 00:30:00,670
