545
00:32:11,020 --> 00:32:12,030
North Clan.

546
00:33:15,980 --> 00:33:16,450
My Lord.

547
00:33:17,140 --> 00:33:19,150
Lei Hongsheng is missing.

548
00:33:20,150 --> 00:33:21,680
Because someone saved him.

549
00:33:22,830 --> 00:33:24,630
The person who saved him just now

550
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:28,520
