551
00:33:28,830 --> 00:33:29,670
But why would the North Clan

552
00:33:29,670 --> 00:33:31,870
save a traitor from the Zichuan family?

553
00:33:32,150 --> 00:33:33,100
Because Lei Hong

554
00:33:33,100 --> 00:33:34,990
has a lot of family information.

555
00:33:35,440 --> 00:33:37,470
If Lei Hong betrays it to the North Clan

556
00:33:37,470 --> 00:33:39,940
to start a dispute between the North Clan and us,

557
00:33:39,940 --> 00:33:41,460
for the North Clan,

558
00:33:42,550 --> 00:33:44,150
he's still got a lot of value.

559
00:33:44,590 --> 00:33:46,720
You mean he's leaning on the North Clan

560
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:49,390
and inciting the North Clan to attack the Zichuan family?

561
00:33:49,390 --> 00:33:50,750
This is just my guess.

562
00:33:51,400 --> 00:33:52,590
I'm afraid

563
00:33:53,160 --> 00:33:55,160
we have to be prepared for the worst.

564
00:33:55,730 --> 00:33:58,450
