00:33:58,830 --> 00:33:59,470
Yes.

566
00:34:00,840 --> 00:34:03,170
It's just that we have to search secretly.

567
00:34:04,790 --> 00:34:05,840
If I'm wrong,

568
00:34:06,370 --> 00:34:09,370
we'll be able to find Lei Hong's hideout soon.

569
00:34:10,389 --> 00:34:12,710
I'm just afraid that I'm right.

570
00:34:14,230 --> 00:34:15,159
Our priority now

571
00:34:15,510 --> 00:34:18,040
is to consolidate the Zichuan family troops'

572
00:34:18,260 --> 00:34:19,989
deployment in Yuanzhou.

573
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:38,280
My Lord.

574
00:34:39,850 --> 00:34:41,110
My Lord, you are awake.

575
00:34:41,590 --> 00:34:42,650
What is this place?

576
00:34:43,639 --> 00:34:46,310
My Lord, as soon as I met the North Clan,

577
00:34:46,790 --> 00:34:48,550
I was arrested

578
00:34:48,949 --> 00:34:50,679
before I could even surrender.

579
00:34:50,909 --> 00:34:51,630
My Lord.

580
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:55,650
Will they kill us next?

581
00:34:58,070 --> 00:35:01,500
No, they need me now.

582
00:35:26,900 --> 00:35:27,460
What?

583
00:35:31,420 --> 00:35:31,890
You...

584
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:04,660
What are you doing?

585
00:36:05,780 --> 00:36:06,180
Don't.

586
00:36:18,470 --> 00:36:18,870
You...

587
00:36:38,450 --> 00:36:39,510
What are you doing?

588
00:36:50,060 --> 00:36:51,500
They are clean now.

589
00:36:51,700 --> 00:36:53,090
Help them clean up.

590
00:36:53,430 --> 00:36:53,990
Yes.

591
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:57,630
My Lord, we're done for.

592
00:37:01,070 --> 00:37:03,960
Not only are we not done for,

593
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:07,390
we're also completely alive.

594
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:16,790
Lei Hong is just a ministerialis of Zichuan.

595
00:37:17,710 --> 00:37:20,170
His subordinates are just a bunch of losers.

596
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:21,900
Why didn't they just kill him?

597
00:37:22,060 --> 00:37:23,590
They actually locked him up

598
00:37:23,750 --> 00:37:25,290
and did the captive ceremony.

599
00:37:25,290 --> 00:37:26,260
This Lei Hong kid...

600
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:26,510
[Ka Dun, Ka Lan]

601
00:37:26,510 --> 00:37:28,480
is not just a captive.

602
00:37:40,790 --> 00:37:41,720
Second brother,

603
00:37:43,290 --> 00:37:46,290
you've always understood Father's intentions best.

604
00:37:46,430 --> 00:37:47,630
What's your opinion?

605
00:37:47,690 --> 00:37:51,620
Brother, you've always been a great warrior, and you're well-versed in military affairs.

606
00:37:51,620 --> 00:37:53,110
This is a military matter.

607
00:37:53,510 --> 00:37:56,160
I think you know it better than I do.

608
00:38:21,100 --> 00:38:21,560
My Lord.

609
00:38:25,390 --> 00:38:26,400
Why are you here?

610
00:38:26,910 --> 00:38:30,780
Today, the Three Central Offices is threatening to intervene in the war in Yuanzhou.

611
00:38:30,780 --> 00:38:32,580
I woud like to come in and listen.

612
00:38:32,950 --> 00:38:35,590
It's against the rules for you to sit in.

613
00:38:37,420 --> 00:38:39,220
All the advisors are here today.

614
00:38:39,390 --> 00:38:41,850
An elder from the Zuoyi Clan was invited too.

615
00:38:41,910 --> 00:38:43,770
Looks like the battle in Yuanzhou

616
00:38:45,630 --> 00:38:47,350
is going to stop.

617
00:38:50,310 --> 00:38:51,630
This is a good thing.

618
00:38:54,430 --> 00:38:54,940
My Lord.

619
00:38:57,860 --> 00:38:59,400
Just wait here.

620
00:39:13,460 --> 00:39:16,150
[Xiao Ping]

621
00:39:17,270 --> 00:39:19,060
[Ma Qin]

622
00:39:20,360 --> 00:39:22,090
[Wang Ge]

623
00:39:23,110 --> 00:39:25,140
[Ma Wei]

624
00:39:30,310 --> 00:39:31,240
Lord Chieftain.

625
00:39:31,660 --> 00:39:33,700
This is the former chief of Zuoyi Clan,

626
00:39:33,700 --> 00:39:34,650
Elder Bunong.

627
00:39:35,320 --> 00:39:37,640
He's also the uncle of the current chief, Budan.

628
00:39:37,640 --> 00:39:37,670
He has a high status and is popular.

629
00:39:37,670 --> 00:39:39,570
[Bunong]

630
00:39:40,670 --> 00:39:41,710
As we all know,

631
00:39:41,710 --> 00:39:44,910
Zuoyi Clan has the most prestige among all tribes in Yuanzhou.

632
00:39:44,910 --> 00:39:46,070
He came here

633
00:39:46,270 --> 00:39:47,980
to represent the Yuanzhou people

634
00:39:47,980 --> 00:39:50,060
to negotiate with the Zichuan family

635
00:39:50,450 --> 00:39:52,090
and sign the peace treaty

636
00:39:52,240 --> 00:39:54,240
to restore peace and prosperity.

637
00:39:59,430 --> 00:40:00,590
Advisor Ma Wei.

638
00:40:03,790 --> 00:40:07,590
You've worked so hard to negotiate this peace.

639
00:40:13,550 --> 00:40:15,070
The war is endless.

640
00:40:15,270 --> 00:40:17,190
It has exhausted our family too much.

641
00:40:17,190 --> 00:40:18,870
As a junior of the Three Central Offices,

642
00:40:18,870 --> 00:40:20,280
I'm willing to help my family

643
00:40:20,280 --> 00:40:21,690
resolve its problems.

644
00:40:22,770 --> 00:40:23,300
Good.

645
00:40:24,220 --> 00:40:27,010
Yes, this battle is long.

646
00:40:27,630 --> 00:40:29,910
I don't think the various clans in Yuanzhou

647
00:40:29,910 --> 00:40:31,670
are doing well.

648
00:40:32,070 --> 00:40:34,440
Lord Chieftain is wise and insightful.

649
00:40:34,670 --> 00:40:37,250
When a battle is fought, who wins?

650
00:40:38,070 --> 00:40:41,510
It's just that the tribes in Yuanzhou are reckless and aggressive.

651
00:40:41,510 --> 00:40:43,080
If not for the war,

652
00:40:43,590 --> 00:40:47,050
they would've caused a lot of troubles for themselves anyway.

653
00:40:47,390 --> 00:40:49,550
It's really hard to control them.

654
00:40:49,950 --> 00:40:51,300
It's a big headache.

655
00:40:51,530 --> 00:40:54,830
No matter how hard it is to control them, you have to control them.

656
00:40:54,830 --> 00:40:56,030
But this battle

657
00:40:56,870 --> 00:40:58,550
did teach us a lesson.

658
00:40:59,360 --> 00:40:59,790
Yes.

659
00:40:59,790 --> 00:41:01,830
Lord Chieftain, you are right.

660
00:41:02,230 --> 00:41:03,470
I'm incompetent.

661
00:41:03,700 --> 00:41:05,700
I'd like to share your worries.

662
00:41:07,470 --> 00:41:10,570
The war has come to an end.

663
00:41:11,070 --> 00:41:13,040
Yuanzhou is a barren land.

664
00:41:13,550 --> 00:41:17,940
If Lord Chieftain allows me to manage it,

665
00:41:18,630 --> 00:41:22,380
you will always come first in all matters.

666
00:41:24,150 --> 00:41:26,430
I can guarantee that

667
00:41:26,830 --> 00:41:28,060
from now on,

668
00:41:28,830 --> 00:41:31,290
all tribes in Yuanzhou will

669
00:41:31,320 --> 00:41:34,310
will respect Zichuan and keep the peace forever.

670
00:41:36,670 --> 00:41:39,190
Elder, I understand what you mean.

671
00:41:40,980 --> 00:41:44,020
You want me to give up Yuanzhou?

672
00:41:46,180 --> 00:41:49,390
Of course not. I'm just managing it.

673
00:41:49,770 --> 00:41:52,150
After all, there's chaos in Yuanzhou.

674
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:55,950
If it's managed by foreigners again,

675
00:41:56,630 --> 00:42:00,190
another war in the future is inevitable.
